article.description: — Duke Deen had 17 points as Troy defeated UT Martin 80-67 on Saturday.
article.headline: Deen, Williams lift Troy past UT Martin 80-67
article.linkText: Deen, Williams lift Troy past UT Martin 80-67
article.story: BOCA RATON, Fla. -- — Duke Deen had 17 points as Troy defeated UT Martin 80-67 on Saturday. Desmond Williams added 16 points for the Trojans, while Efe Odigie chipped in 15. Zay Williams had 11 rebounds for Troy (3-2). KJ Simon had 15 points for the Skyhawks (1-3). KK Curry added 12 points. Koby Jeffries had 11 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
